summary: Verify that --container-storage works
description: |
    This builds a bootc image that embeds an image from the containers-storage
    transport. We call this with --container-storage, supplying a custom container
    storage directory. We verify that both reading the image to be embedded and
    the output bootc container end up using the custom storage.

    Expected results:
      - PASS: 'Container build with custom container store worked'

    Results location:
      output.txt
duration: 60m
id: 778ec5de-1892-4a1a-94e8-040983d7b74f
